The '''Ultraball''' is a type of [[Pokéballs|pokéball]]. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokémon after defeating it if is the highest type of pokeball active and there is a remaining supply in the pokeball selector.


==Details==
===Description===
An excellent pokeball to capture Pokémon with, it provides a +10% catch rate bonus.

